$\\ell \\ge\n\\ell_0$ already $p=\\omega(1/n)$ is sufficient for\n$\\mathcal{F}^\\ell(n,2)$-universality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2019 17:53:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 14:58:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
