form. A pneumatic\nde-ployment mechanism ensures highly compact stowage volumes and minimizes\ncomplexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2019 09:40:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2019 15:03:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2019 03:32:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-18"}
